{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The galaxy is under attack and awaits your valor and skill in the face of looming peril. Join the ranks and let your journey to bring stability and order to the outer borders of the cosmos begin!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2530570/extras/SectionTitle01.png?t=1727452565\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2530570/extras/Gathering.gif?t=1727452565\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Mine asteroids for precious metals and minerals.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Harvest space clouds to discover exotic gases and chemicals.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Salvage wrecks for spare parts and lost artifacts.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2530570/extras/SectionTitle02.png?t=1727452565\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2530570/extras/Combat.gif?t=1727452565\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Engage in battles against local factions for loot, experience, and glory.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Select the right gear to counter your enemies.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Unleash special abilities to turn the tide of battle in your favor.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2530570/extras/SectionTitle03.png?t=1727452565\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2530570/extras/Crew.gif?t=1727452565\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Recruit crew members to assist you on your journey, even while offline.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Craft resources, fuse powerful chipsets, and unlock scientific advancements.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Prioritize your upgrades to suit your playstyle, whether it's active, idle, or both.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2530570/extras/SectionTitle04.png?t=1727452565\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2530570/extras/Upgrade.gif?t=1727452565\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Enhance your ship modules to improve your gathering and combat capabilities.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Level up your crew members to unlock new mechanics and perks</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Join the ranks of the galactic empire and prepare to stand against the impending invasion!</strong></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Completionist","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2530570/609c3cfc7ad9c17daf126bd78c5dc9f8231c3764.jpg"},{"name":"Tycoon","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2530570/d1aaadec5c034d41d5e9b4a4bf7b675add0053fb.jpg"},{"name":"Faster than light","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2530570/a1072e82114cb27d965e35ad0c11bfc7e51739f6.jpg"},{"name":"Dug too deep","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2530570/5f7c19682b6ff161c6d62f75986d73d3460b8df0.jpg"},{"name":"Space vaccum","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2530570/f0ca437f7de96dc94bb2cb13dfae4a0ba6640cf0.jpg"},{"name":"Circular economy","path":"https://cdn.a